#: applications/luci-app-aurora-config/htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/aurora/theme.js:444
msgid ""
"The theme layout uses three layers: background (Background) → page container "
"(Page) → panel card (Panel). The Base Colors variables define each layer's "
"background color (Background) and foreground/text color (Foreground). The "
"primary color (Primary) is mainly used for focused/active states of inputs, "
"selects, radios, checkboxes, and dropdowns, and is also used for key buttons "
"and the page footer."
msgstr "La distribución del tema utiliza tres capas: fondo general (Background) → contenedor de página (Page) → tarjeta del panel (Panel). Las variables de los Colores base definen el fondo (Background) y el color del texto/primer plano (Foreground) de cada capa. El color primario (Primary) se emplea principalmente en los estados activos o enfocados de campos, selectores, botones de radio, casillas y menús desplegables, así como en botones clave y el pie de página."

